      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - The applicant should be a permanent resident of Haryana.\n  - The applicant should currently be residing in Haryana.\n  - The applicant should be between 18 and 70 years.\n  - The applicant should have met with an accident resulting in death or disability.\n\n**Note:**\n\n   1. In case of disability, the claimant must be the disabled person themselves.\n   1. In case of death, the claimants shall be:\n\n\n  - The spouse (if not remarried).\n  - All unmarried children with equal share.\n  - Mother\n  - Father\n  - No other claimant is eligible beyond the above.\n\n",
